commit.message:
PR-108123 gcc/m2/gm2config.h.in

Rebuilt the file gcc/m2/gm2config.h.in with autoheader-2.69.

gcc/m2/ChangeLog:

	* gm2config.h.in: Rebuilt.

Signed-off-by: Gaius Mulley <gaiusmod2@gmail.com>
